Attached is the table of contents of Applied Cryptography.  The book is
suppposed to go to the printer this week, which means everything is set
for an early November release.  The price will be $45 (I think it will
realy be $44.95 or something).  We all wanted a cheaper price, but the
page count got so big that the bean counters at John Wiley & Sons
insisted.  The copyright year is 1994, which seems to make sense to
everyone in the publishing business except me.  I have been told that
you can order it at your local bookstore.  I will post another
announcement when the book is actually shipping.

Bruce

*************************************************************************

                      APPLIED CRYPTORAPHY: 
           PROTOCOLS, ALGORITHMS, AND SOURCE CODE IN C

                        Bruce Schneier   

                    1994, John Wiley & Sons.
                       ISBN: 0-471-59756-2


